data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Beautiful, spacious POOL home on large lot in South Lakeland! You don't want to miss out on this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom move-in ready stunner in a quiet, established neighborhood. Uniquely designed with a show-stopping stone fireplace wall, soaring ceilings, and an atrium-style enclosure in the kitchen! Use this unique space as a bird cage, display case for finer items or collectibles, a terrarium... With a little imagination this could be a showstopper feature! Two screened enclosed patio areas - one by the MASSIVE pool, and one off of the living area for quiet nights out back. Pool access from the dining area AND master bedroom. Shed out back has been used as a workshop, BBQ shack, and storage by previous owners. Shed even has a covered area that stretches toward the pool, great for entertaining! New septic tank and drain field 2021, whole house water filtration system and softener, and new pool pump motor and filter 2022. Nothing to do here but move in and enjoy the rest of pool season!
